image_analysis.description: A photograph of a small bathroom taken through an open doorway. The room contains a white pedestal sink, a white toilet, and a small brown trash can filled with paper. A large mirror is mounted on the wall above the sink, reflecting a doorway and a light fixture in another room. To the right of the sink is a glass-enclosed shower stall with marble-patterned tiling at the base. The floor is covered in small white square tiles. A toothbrush and toothpaste are visible on the edge of the sink.
image_analysis.layout: Interior shot framed by a white door frame on the left and a white wall/door frame on the right.
